\subtree{
\title{Storage Cost Analysis (Aptos Mainnet)}
\pre{\startverb
Pricing assumptions:
- Storage cost: 0.00001 APT per byte
- APT price: $12 USD
- Bytes per tile: 69

Cost formula:
  APT = tiles × 69 × 0.00001
  USD = APT × 12
\stopverb}

